<P>
SRI LANKAN LEADERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 It is "sporting" of you to run a front-page story and color photo, "Daughter 
Taps Mother to Help Lead Sri Lanka" (Nov. 15).It is consistent with your 
progressive reporting of international events -- you perform a useful service 
in a crucial arena. 
