<DOCNO> LA120294-0163 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 104166 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 2, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 1; Column 2; Financial Desk 
</P>
